I'll start by reading the skills list to understand what capabilities are available.

<result>

}
</content>
</document>
</result>

The skills list is currently empty. Let me also check the skills directory.

<function_calls>
<invoke name="Bash">
<parameter name="command">ls -la ~/.claude/skills 2>/dev/null || echo "Skills directory does not exist or is empty"</parameter>
</invoke>
</function_calls>
<result>
total 8
drwxrwxr-x 2 aiscend aiscend 4096 Jun 22 03:42 .
drwxrwxr-x 3 aiscend aiscend 4096 Jun 22 03:42 ..
</result>

The skills directory exists but is empty, and there are no skills registered in the skills.json file.
